      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;firstcharacter&#34;&gt;S&lt;/span&gt;etup!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Introduction&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#introduction&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;TBD&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;set-up-the-compute-engine-instance&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Set up the Compute Engine instance&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#set-up-the-compute-engine-instance&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When setting up a virtual machine, I choose Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS as the operative system.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;First, I install a set of packages which are required by &lt;code&gt;pyenv&lt;/code&gt; for building Python:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#cad3f5;background-color:#24273a;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt update&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt --assume-yes install build-essential libssl-dev zlib1g-dev &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    libbz2-dev libreadline-dev libsqlite3-dev curl &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    libncursesw5-dev xz-utils tk-dev libxml2-dev &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;\&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#8aadf4&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    libxmlsec1-dev libffi-dev liblzma-dev&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Install &lt;code&gt;pyenv&lt;/code&gt; with the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv-installer&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;pyenv&lt;/code&gt; installer&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
